---
import LayoutPrincipal from '../layouts/LayoutPrincipal.astro';
---

<LayoutPrincipal 
  title="Contacto - Distribuidora de Plásticos y Desechables" 
  description="Ponte en contacto con nosotros para pedidos al por mayor, cotizaciones personalizadas o consultas sobre nuestros productos."
>
  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-16 px-6">

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-4 mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block text-xs font-black tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-accent px-4 py-1.5 bg-brand-accent/10 border border-brand-accent/20 rounded-full">
        Hablemos
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-brand-primary text-balance">
        Contáctanos
      </h1>
      <p class="text-brand-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">
        ¿Necesitas cotización para tu empresa? ¿Tienes preguntas sobre disponibilidad o precios mayoristas? Escríbenos y te respondemos a la brevedad.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Main grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-start">

      <!-- Left: Info -->
      <aside class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-5">
        <!-- Contact data -->
        <div class="bg-brand-surface border border-brand-border rounded-2xl p-6 space-y-5 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-base font-extrabold text-brand-primary">Datos de Contacto</h2>

          <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm" role="list">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-accent shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="min-w-0">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-primary">Correo Electrónico</h3>
                <p class="text-brand-secondary truncate">info@catalogobase.com</p>
                <p class="text-brand-secondary truncate">ventas@catalogobase.com</p>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-500 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-primary">Teléfono y WhatsApp</h3>
                <p class="text-brand-secondary">+34&nbsp;900&nbsp;123&nbsp;456</p>
                <p class="text-brand-secondary text-xs mt-0.5">Lun–Vie · 9:00 – 18:00</p>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-500 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-primary">Oficina y Bodega</h3>
                <p class="text-brand-secondary">Av. de la Innovación 42, Planta 3</p>
                <p class="text-brand-secondary">28042 Madrid, España</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Highlight card -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-accent/8 to-purple-500/5 border border-brand-accent/20 rounded-2xl p-5 space-y-2">
          <p class="text-sm font-extrabold text-brand-primary">💬 ¿Pedido urgente?</p>
          <p class="text-brand-secondary text-xs leading-relaxed">
            Puedes contactarnos directamente por WhatsApp para cotizaciones rápidas. Respondemos en menos de 2 horas en horario hábil.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Hours -->
        <div class="bg-brand-surface border border-brand-border rounded-2xl p-5 space-y-3">
          <h3 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-secondary">Horario de Atención</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" role="list">
            {[
              { day: "Lunes – Viernes", hours: "9:00 – 18:00" },
              { day: "Sábado", hours: "9:00 – 13:00" },
              { day: "Domingo", hours: "Cerrado" },
            ].map(row => (
              <li class="flex items-center justify-between text-brand-secondary">
                <span>{row.day}</span>
                <span class="font-bold text-brand-primary tabular-nums">{row.hours}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <!-- Right: Form -->
      <section class="lg:col-span-7 bg-brand-surface border border-brand-border rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm" aria-labelledby="form-heading">
        <h2 id="form-heading" class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-primary mb-6">Enviar un Mensaje</h2>

        <form
          class="space-y-5"
          id="contact-form"
          onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); document.getElementById('form-success').classList.remove('hidden'); this.reset();"
          novalidate
        >
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
            <div class="space-y-1.5">
              <label for="nombre" class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-secondary">
                Nombre Completo <span class="text-brand-accent" aria-label="requerido">*</span>
              </label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="nombre"
                name="nombre"
                required
                autocomplete="name"
                placeholder="Juan Pérez…"
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-brand-border bg-brand-background text-brand-primary placeholder-brand-secondary/50 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-accent/50 focus-visible:border-brand-accent transition-all duration-200 text-sm"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1.5">
              <label for="email" class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-secondary">
                Email <span class="text-brand-accent" aria-label="requerido">*</span>
              </label>
              <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                name="email"
                required
                autocomplete="email"
                spellcheck="false"
                placeholder="juan@empresa.com…"
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-brand-border bg-brand-background text-brand-primary placeholder-brand-secondary/50 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-accent/50 focus-visible:border-brand-accent transition-all duration-200 text-sm"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <label for="empresa" class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-secondary">
              Empresa / Negocio
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="empresa"
              name="empresa"
              autocomplete="organization"
              placeholder="Nombre de tu restaurante o empresa…"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-brand-border bg-brand-background text-brand-primary placeholder-brand-secondary/50 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-accent/50 focus-visible:border-brand-accent transition-all duration-200 text-sm"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <label for="asunto" class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-secondary">
              Asunto <span class="text-brand-accent" aria-label="requerido">*</span>
            </label>
            <select
              id="asunto"
              name="asunto"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-brand-border bg-brand-background text-brand-primary focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-accent/50 focus-visible:border-brand-accent transition-all duration-200 text-sm appearance-none cursor-pointer"
            >
              <option value="" disabled selected>Selecciona un motivo…</option>
              <option value="cotizacion">Solicitar cotización mayorista</option>
              <option value="producto">Consulta sobre un producto</option>
              <option value="pedido">Seguimiento de pedido</option>
              <option value="otro">Otro</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <label for="mensaje" class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-secondary">
              Mensaje <span class="text-brand-accent" aria-label="requerido">*</span>
            </label>
            <textarea
              id="mensaje"
              name="mensaje"
              rows="4"
              required
              placeholder="Cuéntanos tu necesidad: productos que te interesan, cantidades aproximadas, frecuencia de pedido…"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-brand-border bg-brand-background text-brand-primary placeholder-brand-secondary/50 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-accent/50 focus-visible:border-brand-accent transition-all duration-200 text-sm resize-none"
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <button
            type="submit"
            id="submit-btn"
            class="w-full py-4 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-accent/90 text-white font-extrabold shadow-lg shadow-brand-accent/20 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-accent/60 active:scale-[0.98]"
          >
            Enviar Solicitud
          </button>
        </form>

        <!-- Success state -->
        <div id="form-success" class="hidden mt-6 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-xl p-5 text-center space-y-2" aria-live="polite">
          <p class="text-2xl" aria-hidden="true">✅</p>
          <p class="font-extrabold text-brand-primary text-sm">¡Mensaje enviado con éxito!</p>
          <p class="text-brand-secondary text-xs">Te responderemos en menos de 24&nbsp;horas hábiles.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</LayoutPrincipal>
